Chat Edit: 'That seems to have fixed it now, thank you!

One more thing (I think): I would like to add one more color palette to the list of themes--Eldtritch.

The theme information is found here: https://github.com/eldritch-theme

A conf file will need to be added to ~/.config/hypr/themes. There currently isn't a GTK UI theme or icon pack available right now, so I will see if there is something compatible.'
